::DrillBit::

DrillBit enjoyed the kiss, but soon relized that she was drunk out of
her mind.
"Come on, lets get you to you're quorters." He said.
The thought of taking advantage of her crossed his mind, but he quikly
dismissed it.
"You need to rest."
He kissed her on the lips, again. He didn't think there was any harm in
a kiss.
"Come on."
